Let’s break this down step-by-step:

🪞 1. What Splitwise Does Right (Vibes Analysis)

  • Distinctive Color Themes: Each section (dashboard, friends, groups) has its own vibe—custom backgrounds, accent colors, etc.

  • Friendly Fonts & Rounded Corners: Large, readable fonts; playful but professional.

  • Smooth Animations: Subtle, not distracting.

  • Cards, Depth, & Shadows: Content appears layered and lively.

  • Simple, Modern Icons: Minimal but fun.

🟣 2. What We Can Do for Fiinny (Our Options)

A. Per-Screen Color Themes

  • Each core screen (Dashboard, Friends, Groups, Expenses, Profile) has a unique gradient or color accent.

  • Example: Dashboard = purple+blue glass; Friends = green+yellow, Groups = teal+orange, etc.

B. Custom AppBar + Section Headers

  • AppBar adapts to the screen theme.

  • Add subtle icons, mini badges, or emoji in headers.

C. Upgraded Glassmorphism

  • Go bolder with the blur, but add subtle patterns, glows, or gradients behind glass.

  • Try Neumorphism for buttons: soft, extruded surfaces for clickable elements.

D. Background Animations

  • Not just rings—add animated gradients, moving particles, or light sparkles for “living” backgrounds (check out packages like animated_background, rive, or lottie).

E. Fun Touches

  • Use avatars, illustrated icons, or even animated emojis.

  • Empty states with illustrations or “Fiinny tips.”

F. Premium Fonts

  • Use fonts like Inter, Nunito, Manrope, or even fun ones like Baloo for headers.

  • Combine 2 fonts for hierarchy (serious for numbers, playful for titles).

G. Micro-Animations

  • Buttons pop, cards lift, tab transitions, rings animate when updated.

  • simple_animations, flutter_animate.

// ---------------------- Custom Widgets --------------------------

class _AnimatedBackground extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return TweenAnimationBuilder(
      tween: Tween<double>(begin: 0, end: 1),
      duration: const Duration(seconds: 3),
      builder: (context, value, child) {
        return Container(
          decoration: BoxDecoration(
            gradient: LinearGradient(
              colors: [
                Colors.deepPurple.withOpacity(0.9),
                Colors.blueAccent.withOpacity(0.8),
                Colors.black.withOpacity(0.6),
              ],
              begin: Alignment.topLeft,
              end: Alignment.bottomRight,
              stops: [0, value, 1],
            ),
          ),
        );
      },
    );
  }
}

class _NeumorphicCard extends StatelessWidget {
  final String label;
  final String amount;
  final IconData icon;
  final Color color;

  const _NeumorphicCard({
    Key? key,
    required this.label,
    required this.amount,
    required this.icon,
    required this.color,
  }) : super(key: key);

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Container(
      width: 100,
      height: 100,
      margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 4),
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.85),
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(28),
        boxShadow: [
          BoxShadow(
            color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.7),
            offset: Offset(-4, -4),
            blurRadius: 14,
            spreadRadius: 1,
          ),
          BoxShadow(
            color: Colors.black.withOpacity(0.12),
            offset: Offset(5, 5),
            blurRadius: 18,
            spreadRadius: 1,
          ),
        ],
      ),
      child: Column(
        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
        children: [
          Icon(icon, color: color, size: 32),
          const SizedBox(height: 8),
          Text(
            label,
            style: TextStyle(
              fontSize: 15,
              color: Colors.black87,
              fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
              fontFamily: 'Manrope',
            ),
          ),
          const SizedBox(height: 5),
          Text(
            amount,
            style: TextStyle(
              fontSize: 18,
              color: Colors.black87,
              fontWeight: FontWeight.bold,
              fontFamily: 'Manrope',
            ),
          ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}

class _GlassCard extends StatelessWidget {
  final Widget child;

  const _GlassCard({Key? key, required this.child}) : super(key: key);

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Container(
      width: 340,
      height: 190,
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.13),
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(32),
        boxShadow: [
          BoxShadow(
            color: Colors.blueAccent.withOpacity(0.13),
            blurRadius: 24,
            offset: Offset(0, 8),
          ),
        ],
        border: Border.all(color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.32), width: 1.8),
      ),
      child: ClipRRect(
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(32),
        child: BackdropFilter(
          filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 24, sigmaY: 24),
          child: Center(child: child),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

class _NeumorphicButton extends StatelessWidget {
  final IconData icon;
  final String label;
  final VoidCallback onTap;
  final Color color;

  const _NeumorphicButton({
    Key? key,
    required this.icon,
    required this.label,
    required this.onTap,
    required this.color,
  }) : super(key: key);

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return GestureDetector(
      onTap: onTap,
      child: Container(
        width: 110,
        height: 50,
        decoration: BoxDecoration(
          color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.9),
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(18),
          boxShadow: [
            BoxShadow(
              color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.6),
              offset: Offset(-2, -2),
              blurRadius: 10,
              spreadRadius: 1,
            ),
            BoxShadow(
              color: Colors.black.withOpacity(0.10),
              offset: Offset(4, 4),
              blurRadius: 10,
              spreadRadius: 1,
            ),
          ],
        ),
        child: Row(
          mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
          children: [
            Icon(icon, color: color, size: 26),
            const SizedBox(width: 8),
            Text(
              label,
              style: TextStyle(
                fontSize: 16,
                fontFamily: 'Manrope',
                color: Colors.black87,
                fontWeight: FontWeight.bold,
              ),
            ),
          ],
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

  bool _loading = true;
  bool _showFetchButton = false;

  double todayCredit = 0.0;
  double todayDebit = 0.0;
  double totalIncome = 0.0;
  double totalExpense = 0.0;
  double savings = 0.0;

  List<GoalModel> goals = [];
  GoalModel? currentGoal;

  String smartInsight = "";
  String? userAvatar = "assets/images/profile_default.png";

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _initDashboard();
  }

  Future<void> _initDashboard() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);

    try {
      final expenses = await ExpenseService()
          .getExpensesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => ExpenseItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      final incomes = await IncomeService()
          .getIncomesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => IncomeItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      goals = await GoalService().getGoals(widget.userId);
      currentGoal = goals.isNotEmpty ? goals.first : null;

      final now = DateTime.now();
      final today = DateTime(now.year, now.month, now.day);

      todayCredit = incomes.where((t) =>
        t.date.year == today.year &&
        t.date.month == today.month &&
        t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      todayDebit = expenses.where((t) =>
        t.date.year == today.year &&
        t.date.month == today.month &&
        t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalIncome = incomes.where((t) =>
        t.date.month == now.month &&
        t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalExpense = expenses.where((t) =>
        t.date.month == now.month &&
        t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      savings = totalIncome - totalExpense;
      _showFetchButton = incomes.isEmpty && expenses.isEmpty;
      _generateSmartInsight();
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Dashboard error: $e")),
      );
    }

    setState(() => _loading = false);
  }

  Future<void> _fetchEmailTx() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);
    try {
      await GmailService().fetchAndStoreTransactionsFromGmail(widget.userId);
      await _initDashboard();
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Fetched transactions from email!"), backgroundColor: Colors.green),
      );
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Failed to fetch email data: $e"), backgroundColor: Colors.red),
      );
    } finally {
      setState(() => _loading = false);
    }
  }

  void _generateSmartInsight() {
    if (totalIncome == 0 && totalExpense == 0) {
      smartInsight = "Add your first transaction or fetch from Gmail to get insights!";
    } else if (totalExpense > totalIncome) {
      smartInsight = "You're spending more than you earn this month. Be careful!";
    } else if (savings / (totalIncome == 0 ? 1 : totalIncome) > 0.3) {
      smartInsight = "Great! You’ve saved over 30% of your income this month.";
    } else if (currentGoal != null && currentGoal!.targetAmount > 0 && savings > 0) {
      double months = ((currentGoal!.targetAmount - currentGoal!.savedAmount) / (savings == 0 ? 1 : savings)).clamp(1, 36);
      smartInsight = "At this pace, you'll reach your goal '${currentGoal!.title}' in about ${months.toStringAsFixed(0)} months!";
    } else {
      smartInsight = "Keep tracking your expenses and save more!";
    }
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      extendBodyBehindAppBar: true, // For glass AppBar look
      appBar: PreferredSize(
        preferredSize: const Size.fromHeight(62),
        child: GlassAppBar(userAvatar: userAvatar),
      ),
      body: Stack(
        children: [
          const AnimatedGlassBackground(),
          _loading
              ? const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator())
              : RefreshIndicator(
                  onRefresh: _initDashboard,
                  child: ListView(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 100, bottom: 20, left: 16, right: 16),
                    children: [
                      // Neumorphic Stats Row
                      Row(
                        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly,
                        children: [
                          NeumorphicSummaryTile(
                            label: "Credit",
                            value: todayCredit,
                            icon: Icons.arrow_downward_rounded,
                            color: Colors.greenAccent,
                          ),
                          NeumorphicSummaryTile(
                            label: "Debit",
                            value: todayDebit,
                            icon: Icons.arrow_upward_rounded,
                            color: Colors.redAccent,
                          ),
                        ],
                      ),
                      const SizedBox(height: 18),
                      // Fetch Email Button
                      if (_showFetchButton || true)
                        Padding(
                          padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 4.0),
                          child: ElevatedButton.icon(
                            style: ElevatedButton.styleFrom(
                              backgroundColor: Colors.deepPurple,
                              padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 13),
                              shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
                                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(15),
                              ),
                              elevation: 8,
                            ),
                            icon: const Icon(Icons.mail_rounded, color: Colors.white),
                            label: const Text(
                              "Fetch Email Data",
                              style: TextStyle(color: Colors.white, fontSize: 16),
                            ),
                            onPressed: _fetchEmailTx,
                          ),
                        ),
                      SmartInsightCard(
                        income: totalIncome,
                        expense: totalExpense,
                        savings: savings,
                        goal: currentGoal,
                      ),
                      const SizedBox(height: 18),
                      Row(
                        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween,
                        children: [
                          const Text(
                            "Your Goals",
                            style: TextStyle(
                              fontSize: 18,
                              fontWeight: FontWeight.w700,
                              color: Colors.white,
                              letterSpacing: 0.2,
                            ),
                          ),
                          TextButton(
                            onPressed: () => Navigator.pushNamed(context, '/goals'),
                            child: const Text("View All", style: TextStyle(fontWeight: FontWeight.w500)),
                          ),
                        ],
                      ),
                      if (goals.isEmpty)
                        const Padding(
                          padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
                          child: Text(
                            "No goals added yet! Tap to add your first.",

                        ),
                      ...goals.take(2).map((g) => GlassGoalCard(goal: g)),
                      if (goals.length > 2)
                        Center(

class AnimatedGlassBackground extends StatelessWidget {
  const AnimatedGlassBackground({super.key});
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return TweenAnimationBuilder<double>(
      tween: Tween<double>(begin: 0.0, end: 1.0),
      duration: const Duration(seconds: 3),
      builder: (context, value, child) => Container(
        decoration: BoxDecoration(
          gradient: LinearGradient(
            colors: [
              Colors.deepPurple.withOpacity(0.85),
              Colors.blueAccent.withOpacity(0.8),
              Colors.black.withOpacity(0.6),
            ],
            begin: Alignment.topLeft,
            end: Alignment.bottomRight,
            stops: [0, value, 1],
          ),
        ),
        child: BackdropFilter(
          filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 16, sigmaY: 16),
          child: Container(color: Colors.transparent),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

class NeumorphicSummaryTile extends StatelessWidget {

  final double value;
  final IconData icon;
  final Color color;
  const NeumorphicSummaryTile({
    required this.label,
    required this.value,
    required this.icon,
    required this.color,
    super.key,
  });

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Container(
      width: 138,
      height: 94,
      margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 5),
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.95),

          BoxShadow(
            color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.7),
            offset: const Offset(-4, -4),
            blurRadius: 14,
            spreadRadius: 1,
          ),
          BoxShadow(
            color: Colors.black.withOpacity(0.13),
            offset: const Offset(6, 6),

            spreadRadius: 1,

✨ Step-by-Step:

1. app_theme.dart

Add this to your app_theme.dart (or create one if not present):

dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

// Main palette for Tiffany Blue/Mint/Teal theme
const Color tiffanyBlue = Color(0xFF81e6d9);
const Color mintGreen = Color(0xFFb9f5d8);
const Color deepTeal   = Color(0xFF09857a);
const Color lightMint  = Color(0xFFF2FFFA);
const Color coral      = Color(0xFFFFD6A5); // accent

final ThemeData freshTheme = ThemeData(
  brightness: Brightness.light,
  primaryColor: tiffanyBlue,
  scaffoldBackgroundColor: lightMint,
  appBarTheme: AppBarTheme(
    backgroundColor: tiffanyBlue,
    elevation: 0,
    iconTheme: IconThemeData(color: deepTeal),
    titleTextStyle: TextStyle(
      color: deepTeal,
      fontWeight: FontWeight.bold,
      fontSize: 22,
      fontFamily: 'Manrope',
      letterSpacing: 0.5,
    ),
  ),
  floatingActionButtonTheme: FloatingActionButtonThemeData(
    backgroundColor: mintGreen,
    foregroundColor: deepTeal,
    elevation: 6,
  ),
  cardColor: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.85),
  textTheme: TextTheme(
    headline6: TextStyle(color: deepTeal, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold),
    bodyText2: TextStyle(color: deepTeal),
  ),
  buttonTheme: ButtonThemeData(
    buttonColor: deepTeal,
    textTheme: ButtonTextTheme.primary,
    shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16)),
  ),
  colorScheme: ColorScheme.fromSwatch().copyWith(
    secondary: mintGreen,
    primary: tiffanyBlue,
    surface: Colors.white,
    onPrimary: deepTeal,
    onSurface: deepTeal,
  ),
);

2. Update your theme_provider.dart like this:

dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'app_theme.dart';

enum FiinnyTheme { light, dark, glass, fresh } // add fresh

class ThemeProvider extends ChangeNotifier {
  FiinnyTheme _theme = FiinnyTheme.fresh; // set fresh as default

  FiinnyTheme get theme => _theme;

  ThemeData get themeData {
    switch (_theme) {
      case FiinnyTheme.dark:
        return darkTheme;
      case FiinnyTheme.glass:
        return glassTheme;
      case FiinnyTheme.fresh:
        return freshTheme;
      default:
        return appTheme;
    }
  }

  bool get isDarkMode => _theme == FiinnyTheme.dark;

  void toggleTheme() {
    _theme = FiinnyTheme.values[(_theme.index + 1) % FiinnyTheme.values.length];
    notifyListeners();
  }

  void setTheme(FiinnyTheme newTheme) {
    _theme = newTheme;
    notifyListeners();
  }
}

3. That’s it!

  • All your screens using Theme.of(context) will automatically take the new palette!

  • If you want custom widget backgrounds/gradients (e.g. animated background), use the same color constants for full visual consistency.

Great catch!
This is a common issue with Flutter 3.x+:
headline6 and bodyText2 are deprecated and now replaced by titleLarge and bodyMedium respectively in the latest Flutter [Material 3] typography.

🚦 How to Fix:

Just change:

dart
textTheme: TextTheme(
  headline6: TextStyle(...),
  bodyText2: TextStyle(...),
),

to:

dart
textTheme: TextTheme(
  titleLarge: TextStyle(color: deepTeal, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold),
  bodyMedium: TextStyle(color: deepTeal),
),

Here’s the corrected section:

dart
  textTheme: TextTheme(
    titleLarge: TextStyle(color: deepTeal, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold),
    bodyMedium: TextStyle(color: deepTeal),
  ),

No more red lines!
You can update this in all your theme files for full Material 3 compliance.

import 'dart:ui';
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

// Color palette (sync with app_theme.dart for consistency)
const Color tiffanyBlue = Color(0xFF81e6d9);
const Color mintGreen = Color(0xFFb9f5d8);
const Color deepTeal = Color(0xFF09857a);
const Color lightMint = Color(0xFFF2FFFA);
const Color coral = Color(0xFFFFD6A5);

class DashboardScreen extends StatefulWidget {
  final String userId;
  const DashboardScreen({required this.userId, Key? key}) : super(key: key);

  @override
  State<DashboardScreen> createState() => _DashboardScreenState();
}

class _DashboardScreenState extends State<DashboardScreen> {
  bool _loading = true;
  bool _showFetchButton = false;

  double todayCredit = 0.0;
  double todayDebit = 0.0;
  double totalIncome = 0.0;
  double totalExpense = 0.0;
  double savings = 0.0;

  List<GoalModel> goals = [];
  GoalModel? currentGoal;

  String smartInsight = "";
  String? userAvatar = "assets/images/profile_default.png";

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _initDashboard();
  }

  Future<void> _initDashboard() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);

    try {
      final expenses = await ExpenseService()
          .getExpensesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => ExpenseItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      final incomes = await IncomeService()
          .getIncomesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => IncomeItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      goals = await GoalService().getGoals(widget.userId);
      currentGoal = goals.isNotEmpty ? goals.first : null;

      final now = DateTime.now();
      final today = DateTime(now.year, now.month, now.day);

      todayCredit = incomes.where((t) =>
      t.date.year == today.year &&
          t.date.month == today.month &&
          t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      todayDebit = expenses.where((t) =>
      t.date.year == today.year &&
          t.date.month == today.month &&
          t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalIncome = incomes.where((t) =>
      t.date.month == now.month &&
          t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalExpense = expenses.where((t) =>
      t.date.month == now.month &&
          t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      savings = totalIncome - totalExpense;
      _showFetchButton = incomes.isEmpty && expenses.isEmpty;
      _generateSmartInsight();
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Dashboard error: $e")),
      );
    }

    setState(() => _loading = false);
  }

  Future<void> _fetchEmailTx() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);
    try {
      await GmailService().fetchAndStoreTransactionsFromGmail(widget.userId);
      await _initDashboard();
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Fetched transactions from email!"), backgroundColor: Colors.green),
      );
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Failed to fetch email data: $e"), backgroundColor: Colors.red),
      );
    } finally {
      setState(() => _loading = false);
    }
  }

  void _generateSmartInsight() {
    if (totalIncome == 0 && totalExpense == 0) {
      smartInsight = "Add your first transaction or fetch from Gmail to get insights!";
    } else if (totalExpense > totalIncome) {
      smartInsight = "You're spending more than you earn this month. Be careful!";
    } else if (savings / (totalIncome == 0 ? 1 : totalIncome) > 0.3) {
      smartInsight = "Great! You’ve saved over 30% of your income this month.";
    } else if (currentGoal != null && currentGoal!.targetAmount > 0 && savings > 0) {
      double months = ((currentGoal!.targetAmount - currentGoal!.savedAmount) / (savings == 0 ? 1 : savings)).clamp(1, 36);
      smartInsight = "At this pace, you'll reach your goal '${currentGoal!.title}' in about ${months.toStringAsFixed(0)} months!";
    } else {
      smartInsight = "Keep tracking your expenses and save more!";
    }
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      extendBodyBehindAppBar: true,
      appBar: PreferredSize(
        preferredSize: const Size.fromHeight(70),
        child: _GlassAppBar(userAvatar: userAvatar),
      ),
      body: Stack(
        children: [
          const _AnimatedMintBackground(),
          _loading
              ? const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator())
              : RefreshIndicator(
            onRefresh: _initDashboard,
            child: ListView(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 110, bottom: 24, left: 14, right: 14),
              children: [
                // Sexy Stat Row
                Row(
                  mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly,
                  children: [
                    _NeumorphicStatCard(
                      label: "Credit",
                      value: todayCredit,
                      icon: Icons.arrow_downward_rounded,
                      color: deepTeal,
                    ),
                    _NeumorphicStatCard(
                      label: "Debit",
                      value: todayDebit,
                      icon: Icons.arrow_upward_rounded,
                      color: coral,
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
                const SizedBox(height: 18),
                // Fetch Email Button
                if (_showFetchButton || true)
                  Padding(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 4.0),
                    child: ElevatedButton.icon(
                      style: ElevatedButton.styleFrom(
                        backgroundColor: deepTeal,
                        foregroundColor: Colors.white,
                        padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 13),
                        shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
                          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(15),
                        ),
                        elevation: 8,
                      ),
                      icon: const Icon(Icons.mail_rounded, color: Colors.white),
                      label: const Text(
                        "Fetch Email Data",
                        style: TextStyle(color: Colors.white, fontSize: 16),
                      ),
                      onPressed: _fetchEmailTx,
                    ),
                  ),
                SmartInsightCard(
                  income: totalIncome,
                  expense: totalExpense,
                  savings: savings,
                  goal: currentGoal,
                ),
                const SizedBox(height: 18),
                Row(
                  mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween,
                  children: [
                    const Text(
                      "Your Goals",
                      style: TextStyle(
                        fontSize: 18,
                        fontWeight: FontWeight.w700,
                        color: deepTeal,
                        letterSpacing: 0.2,
                      ),
                    ),
                    TextButton(
                      onPressed: () => Navigator.pushNamed(context, '/goals'),
                      child: const Text("View All", style: TextStyle(fontWeight: FontWeight.w500, color: deepTeal)),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
                if (goals.isEmpty)
                  const Padding(
                    padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
                    child: Text(
                      "No goals added yet! Tap to add your first.",
                      style: TextStyle(color: Colors.teal),
                    ),
                  ),
                ...goals.take(2).map((g) => _GlassGoalCard(goal: g)),
                if (goals.length > 2)
                  Center(

class _AnimatedMintBackground extends StatelessWidget {
  const _AnimatedMintBackground({super.key});
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return TweenAnimationBuilder<double>(
      tween: Tween<double>(begin: 0.0, end: 1.0),
      duration: const Duration(seconds: 2),
      builder: (context, value, child) => Container(
        decoration: BoxDecoration(
          gradient: LinearGradient(
            colors: [
              tiffanyBlue,
              mintGreen,
              Colors.white.withOpacity(0.85),
            ],
            begin: Alignment.topLeft,
            end: Alignment.bottomRight,
            stops: [0, value, 1],
          ),
        ),
        child: BackdropFilter(
          filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 14, sigmaY: 14),
          child: Container(color: Colors.transparent),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

// Tiffany/Mint palette
const Color tiffanyBlue = Color(0xFF81e6d9);
const Color mintGreen = Color(0xFFb9f5d8);
const Color deepTeal = Color(0xFF09857a);
const Color lightMint = Color(0xFFF2FFFA);

class DashboardScreen extends StatefulWidget {
  final String userId;
  const DashboardScreen({required this.userId, Key? key}) : super(key: key);

  @override
  State<DashboardScreen> createState() => _DashboardScreenState();
}

class _DashboardScreenState extends State<DashboardScreen> {
  bool _loading = true;
  bool _showFetchButton = false;

  double todayCredit = 0.0;
  double todayDebit = 0.0;
  double totalIncome = 0.0;
  double totalExpense = 0.0;
  double savings = 0.0;

  List<GoalModel> goals = [];
  GoalModel? currentGoal;

  String smartInsight = "";
  String? userAvatar = "assets/images/profile_default.png";

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _initDashboard();
  }

  Future<void> _initDashboard() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);

    try {
      final expenses = await ExpenseService()
          .getExpensesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => ExpenseItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      final incomes = await IncomeService()
          .getIncomesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => IncomeItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      goals = await GoalService().getGoals(widget.userId);
      currentGoal = goals.isNotEmpty ? goals.first : null;

      final now = DateTime.now();
      final today = DateTime(now.year, now.month, now.day);

      todayCredit = incomes.where((t) =>
      t.date.year == today.year &&
          t.date.month == today.month &&
          t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      todayDebit = expenses.where((t) =>
      t.date.year == today.year &&
          t.date.month == today.month &&
          t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalIncome = incomes.where((t) =>
      t.date.month == now.month &&
          t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalExpense = expenses.where((t) =>
      t.date.month == now.month &&
          t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      savings = totalIncome - totalExpense;
      _showFetchButton = incomes.isEmpty && expenses.isEmpty;
      _generateSmartInsight();
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Dashboard error: $e")),
      );
    }

    setState(() => _loading = false);
  }

  Future<void> _fetchEmailTx() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);
    try {
      await GmailService().fetchAndStoreTransactionsFromGmail(widget.userId);
      await _initDashboard();
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Fetched transactions from email!"), backgroundColor: Colors.green),
      );
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Failed to fetch email data: $e"), backgroundColor: Colors.red),
      );
    } finally {
      setState(() => _loading = false);
    }
  }

  void _generateSmartInsight() {
    if (totalIncome == 0 && totalExpense == 0) {
      smartInsight = "Add your first transaction or fetch from Gmail to get insights!";
    } else if (totalExpense > totalIncome) {
      smartInsight = "You're spending more than you earn this month. Be careful!";
    } else if (savings / (totalIncome == 0 ? 1 : totalIncome) > 0.3) {
      smartInsight = "Great! You’ve saved over 30% of your income this month.";
    } else if (currentGoal != null && currentGoal!.targetAmount > 0 && savings > 0) {
      double months = ((currentGoal!.targetAmount - currentGoal!.savedAmount) / (savings == 0 ? 1 : savings)).clamp(1, 36);
      smartInsight = "At this pace, you'll reach your goal '${currentGoal!.title}' in about ${months.toStringAsFixed(0)} months!";
    } else {
      smartInsight = "Keep tracking your expenses and save more!";
    }
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      extendBodyBehindAppBar: true,
      appBar: PreferredSize(
        preferredSize: const Size.fromHeight(82),
        child: _GlassAppBarWithProfile(userAvatar: userAvatar),
      ),
      body: Stack(
        children: [
          const _AnimatedMintBackground(),
          _loading
              ? const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator())
              : RefreshIndicator(
            onRefresh: _initDashboard,
            child: ListView(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 120, bottom: 24, left: 14, right: 14),
              children: [
                // Stat Cards Row (Overflow Safe)
                Padding(
                  padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 3),
                  child: Row(
                    mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly,
                    children: [
                      _NeumorphicStatCard(
                        label: "Credit",
                        value: todayCredit,
                        icon: Icons.arrow_downward_rounded,
                        color: deepTeal,
                      ),
                      _NeumorphicStatCard(
                        label: "Debit",
                        value: todayDebit,
                        icon: Icons.arrow_upward_rounded,
                        color: coral,
                      ),
                    ],
                  ),
                ),
                const SizedBox(height: 18),
                if (_showFetchButton || true)
                  Padding(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 4.0),
                    child: ElevatedButton.icon(
                      style: ElevatedButton.styleFrom(
                        backgroundColor: deepTeal,
                        foregroundColor: Colors.white,
                        padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 13),
                        shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
                          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(15),
                        ),
                        elevation: 8,
                      ),
                      icon: const Icon(Icons.mail_rounded, color: Colors.white),
                      label: const Text(
                        "Fetch Email Data",
                        style: TextStyle(color: Colors.white, fontSize: 16),
                      ),
                      onPressed: _fetchEmailTx,
                    ),
                  ),
                SmartInsightCard(
                  income: totalIncome,
                  expense: totalExpense,
                  savings: savings,
                  goal: currentGoal,
                ),
                const SizedBox(height: 18),
                Row(
                  mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween,
                  children: [
                    const Text(
                      "Your Goals",
                      style: TextStyle(
                        fontSize: 18,
                        fontWeight: FontWeight.w700,
                        color: deepTeal,
                        letterSpacing: 0.2,
                      ),
                    ),
                    TextButton(
                      onPressed: () => Navigator.pushNamed(context, '/goals'),
                      child: const Text("View All", style: TextStyle(fontWeight: FontWeight.w500, color: deepTeal)),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
                if (goals.isEmpty)
                  const Padding(
                    padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
                    child: Text(
                      "No goals added yet! Tap to add your first.",
                      style: TextStyle(color: Colors.teal),
                    ),
                  ),
                ...goals.take(2).map((g) => _GlassGoalCard(goal: g)),
                if (goals.length > 2)
                  Center(
                    child: Text(
                      "+${goals.length - 2} more goals...",
                      style: const TextStyle(color: deepTeal, fontWeight: FontWeight.w500),
                    ),
                  ),
                const SizedBox(height: 80),
              ],
            ),
          ),
        ],
      ),
      floatingActionButton: _MintFab(onRefresh: _initDashboard),
    );
  }
}

class _AnimatedMintBackground extends StatelessWidget {
  const _AnimatedMintBackground({super.key});
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return TweenAnimationBuilder<double>(
      tween: Tween<double>(begin: 0.0, end: 1.0),
      duration: const Duration(seconds: 2),
      builder: (context, value, child) => Container(
        decoration: BoxDecoration(
          gradient: LinearGradient(
            colors: [
              tiffanyBlue,
              mintGreen,
              Colors.white.withOpacity(0.85),
            ],
            begin: Alignment.topLeft,
            end: Alignment.bottomRight,
            stops: [0, value, 1],
          ),
        ),
        child: BackdropFilter(
          filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 14, sigmaY: 14),
          child: Container(color: Colors.transparent),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }

class DashboardScreen extends StatefulWidget {
  final String userId;
  const DashboardScreen({required this.userId, Key? key}) : super(key: key);

  @override
  State<DashboardScreen> createState() => _DashboardScreenState();
}

class _DashboardScreenState extends State<DashboardScreen> {
  bool _loading = true;
  bool _showFetchButton = false;

  double todayCredit = 0.0;
  double todayDebit = 0.0;
  double totalIncome = 0.0;
  double totalExpense = 0.0;
  double savings = 0.0;

  List<GoalModel> goals = [];
  GoalModel? currentGoal;

  String smartInsight = "";
  String? userAvatar = "assets/images/profile_default.png";

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _initDashboard();
  }

  Future<void> _initDashboard() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);

    try {
      final expenses = await ExpenseService()
          .getExpensesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => ExpenseItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      final incomes = await IncomeService()
          .getIncomesCollection(widget.userId)
          .orderBy('date', descending: true)
          .get()
          .then((snap) => snap.docs.map((doc) => IncomeItem.fromJson(doc.data())).toList());

      goals = await GoalService().getGoals(widget.userId);
      print('[Dashboard] Goals fetched: ${goals.length} for userId: ${widget.userId}');
      currentGoal = goals.isNotEmpty ? goals.first : null;

      final now = DateTime.now();
      final today = DateTime(now.year, now.month, now.day);

      todayCredit = incomes.where((t) =>
      t.date.year == today.year &&
          t.date.month == today.month &&
          t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      todayDebit = expenses.where((t) =>
      t.date.year == today.year &&
          t.date.month == today.month &&
          t.date.day == today.day
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalIncome = incomes.where((t) =>
      t.date.month == now.month &&
          t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      totalExpense = expenses.where((t) =>
      t.date.month == now.month &&
          t.date.year == now.year
      ).fold(0.0, (a, b) => a + b.amount);

      savings = totalIncome - totalExpense;
      _showFetchButton = incomes.isEmpty && expenses.isEmpty;
      _generateSmartInsight();
    } catch (e) {
      print('[Dashboard] ERROR: $e');
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Dashboard error: $e")),
      );
    }

    setState(() => _loading = false);
  }

  Future<void> _fetchEmailTx() async {
    setState(() => _loading = true);
    try {
      await GmailService().fetchAndStoreTransactionsFromGmail(widget.userId);
      await _initDashboard();
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Fetched transactions from email!"), backgroundColor: Colors.green),
      );
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
        SnackBar(content: Text("Failed to fetch email data: $e"), backgroundColor: Colors.red),
      );
    } finally {
      setState(() => _loading = false);
    }
  }

  void _generateSmartInsight() {
    if (totalIncome == 0 && totalExpense == 0) {
      smartInsight = "Add your first transaction or fetch from Gmail to get insights!";
    } else if (totalExpense > totalIncome) {
      smartInsight = "You're spending more than you earn this month. Be careful!";
    } else if (savings / (totalIncome == 0 ? 1 : totalIncome) > 0.3) {
      smartInsight = "Great! You’ve saved over 30% of your income this month.";
    } else if (currentGoal != null && currentGoal!.targetAmount > 0 && savings > 0) {
      double months = ((currentGoal!.targetAmount - currentGoal!.savedAmount) / (savings == 0 ? 1 : savings)).clamp(1, 36);
      smartInsight = "At this pace, you'll reach your goal '${currentGoal!.title}' in about ${months.toStringAsFixed(0)} months!";
    } else {
      smartInsight = "Keep tracking your expenses and save more!";
    }
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      extendBodyBehindAppBar: true,
      appBar: PreferredSize(
        preferredSize: const Size.fromHeight(94), // Taller AppBar!
        child: _GlassAppBarWithProfile(userAvatar: userAvatar),
      ),
      body: Stack(
        children: [
          const _AnimatedMintBackground(),
          _loading
              ? const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator())
              : RefreshIndicator(
            onRefresh: _initDashboard,
            child: ListView(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 132, bottom: 24, left: 12, right: 12),
              children: [
                // Stat Cards Row (no overflow ever)
                Row(
                  mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly,
                  mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.max,
                  children: [
                    Flexible(
                      child: _NeumorphicStatCard(
                        label: "Credit",
                        value: todayCredit,
                        icon: Icons.arrow_downward_rounded,
                        color: deepTeal,
                      ),
                    ),
                    const SizedBox(width: 10),
                    Flexible(
                      child: _NeumorphicStatCard(
                        label: "Debit",
                        value: todayDebit,
                        icon: Icons.arrow_upward_rounded,
                        color: coral,
                      ),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
                const SizedBox(height: 18),
                if (_showFetchButton || true)
                  Padding(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 4.0),
                    child: ElevatedButton.icon(
                      style: ElevatedButton.styleFrom(
                        backgroundColor: deepTeal,
                        foregroundColor: Colors.white,
                        padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 13),
                        shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
                          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(15),
                        ),
                        elevation: 8,
                      ),
                      icon: const Icon(Icons.mail_rounded, color: Colors.white),
                      label: const Text(
                        "Fetch Email Data",
                        style: TextStyle(color: Colors.white, fontSize: 16),
                      ),
                      onPressed: _fetchEmailTx,
                    ),
                  ),
                SmartInsightCard(
                  income: totalIncome,
                  expense: totalExpense,
                  savings: savings,
                  goal: currentGoal,
                ),
                const SizedBox(height: 18),
                Row(
                  mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween,
                  children: [
                    const Text(
                      "Your Goals",
                      style: TextStyle(
                        fontSize: 18,
                        fontWeight: FontWeight.w700,
                        color: deepTeal,
                        letterSpacing: 0.2,
                      ),

                    TextButton(

class _NeumorphicStatCard extends StatelessWidget {
  final String label;
  final double value;
  final IconData icon;
  final Color color;
  const _NeumorphicStatCard({
    required this.label,
    required this.value,
    required this.icon,
    required this.color,
    super.key,
  });

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Container(
      // Shrinks if needed, always fits
      constraints: const BoxConstraints(maxWidth: 150, minWidth: 95),
      height: 82,
      margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 3),
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.96),
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(21),
        boxShadow: [
          BoxShadow(
            color: mintGreen.withOpacity(0.33),
            offset: const Offset(-3, -3),
            blurRadius: 12,
            spreadRadius: 1,
          ),
          BoxShadow(
            color: Colors.black.withOpacity(0.07),
            offset: const Offset(5, 5),
            blurRadius: 13,
            spreadRadius: 1,
          ),
        ],
      ),
      child: Center(
        child: FittedBox(
          fit: BoxFit.scaleDown,
          child: Column(
            mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
            children: [
              Icon(icon, color: color, size: 27),
              const SizedBox(height: 5),
              Text(label, style: TextStyle(fontWeight: FontWeight.bold, color: color, fontSize: 13)),
              const SizedBox(height: 2),
              Text("₹${value.toStringAsFixed(0)}",
                  style: TextStyle(fontWeight: FontWeight.bold, color: deepTeal, fontSize: 16)),
            ],
          ),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

// Animated Mint Background

class _AnimatedMintBackground extends StatelessWidget {
  const _AnimatedMintBackground({super.key});
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return TweenAnimationBuilder<double>(
      tween: Tween<double>(begin: 0.0, end: 1.0),
      duration: const Duration(seconds: 2),
      builder: (context, value, child) => Container(
        decoration: BoxDecoration(
          gradient: LinearGradient(
            colors: [
              tiffanyBlue,
              mintGreen,
              Colors.white.withOpacity(0.85),
            ],
            begin: Alignment.topLeft,
            end: Alignment.bottomRight,
            stops: [0, value, 1],
          ),
        ),
        child: BackdropFilter(
          filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 14, sigmaY: 14),
          child: Container(color: Colors.transparent),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

🎨 Fiinny Theme Selector Plan (2024+ Ready!)

1. Define Multiple Themes in app_theme.dart

  • Build all theme variants in one file:

    • freshTheme (Tiffany/Mint)

    • royalTheme (Royal Blue/Gold)

    • sunnyTheme (Coral/Lemon)

    • midnightTheme (Deep Blue/Black)

    • classicTheme (Purple)

    • pureDarkTheme (Black/White minimalist)

    • lightMinimalTheme (White background, dark text)

  • Each theme is a ThemeData object—add more anytime!

2. Expand Theme Enum and ThemeProvider

  • Add a value for each theme in your enum:

    dart
    enum FiinnyTheme { fresh, royal, sunny, midnight, classic, pureDark, lightMinimal }

  • In ThemeProvider, add a ThemeData get themeData switch for each theme.

  • When you want to add a new theme in the future, just add it to both enum and switch—no code changes anywhere else!

3. Theme Selector Widget (for Onboarding & Profile)

  • Build a reusable ThemeSelectorWidget (grid or list of clickable cards).

  • Each card shows a preview (color + sample UI + name).

  • Tapping a card calls ThemeProvider.setTheme(selectedTheme).

  • You can use this widget in both onboarding and in profile/settings.

4. Persistent Theme Storage

  • Use SharedPreferences (or Firestore) to save the user’s chosen theme.

  • On app startup, read the saved value and call ThemeProvider.setTheme(...) to restore.

  • This way, the user’s favorite theme always loads instantly.

5. Live Theme Update Across the App

  • When the user selects a theme, the app updates instantly everywhere (thanks to Provider).

  • All screens using Theme.of(context) or theme colors/fonts update automatically.

  • No need to manually update each screen—future themes will always “just work”.

Add as Many Themes as You Want!

  • Just add a new palette and name to your files.

  • Users will see it next time they open the Theme Selector (onboarding or profile).

  • Example: “Add Dark/Light/Black-and-White” in 1 minute—no extra wiring needed!

    FiinnyTheme.fresh: "Fresh Mint",
    FiinnyTheme.royal: "Royal Blue",
    FiinnyTheme.sunny: "Sunny Coral",
    FiinnyTheme.midnight: "Midnight",
    FiinnyTheme.classic: "Classic Purple",
    FiinnyTheme.pureDark: "Pure Dark",
    FiinnyTheme.lightMinimal: "Minimal Light",
  };

  final Map<FiinnyTheme, List<Color>> themeSwatches = {
    FiinnyTheme.fresh: [Color(0xFF81e6d9), Color(0xFFb9f5d8), Color(0xFF09857a)],
    FiinnyTheme.royal: [Color(0xFF2E3192), Color(0xFFF8B500), Color(0xFFFFFFFF)],
    FiinnyTheme.sunny: [Color(0xFFFFF475), Color(0xFFFFD6A5), Color(0xFFFF7F50)],
    FiinnyTheme.midnight: [Color(0xFF131E2A), Color(0xFF2D4D5B), Color(0xFF00ADB5)],
    FiinnyTheme.classic: [Color(0xFF7C3AED), Color(0xFFB794F4), Color(0xFFF6F1FF)],
    FiinnyTheme.pureDark: [Colors.black, Colors.white, Colors.grey],
    FiinnyTheme.lightMinimal: [Colors.white, Colors.black, Colors.grey[300]!],
  };

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    final themeProvider = Provider.of<ThemeProvider>(context);
    return Padding(
      padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 26, horizontal: 16),
      child: Column(
        mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min,
        children: [
          const Text(
            "Choose Your Theme",
            style: TextStyle(fontSize: 22, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold, letterSpacing: 0.3),
          ),
          const SizedBox(height: 24),
          GridView.count(
            shrinkWrap: true,
            crossAxisCount: 2,
            mainAxisSpacing: 24,
            crossAxisSpacing: 16,
            childAspectRatio: 1.22,
            physics: const NeverScrollableScrollPhysics(),
            children: FiinnyTheme.values.map((fiinnyTheme) {
              return GestureDetector(
                onTap: () async {
                  themeProvider.setTheme(fiinnyTheme);
                  // Optional: Save theme to SharedPreferences here if not handled in provider.
                  Navigator.of(context).maybePop();
                },
                child: Card(
                  shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(20)),
                  elevation: themeProvider.theme == fiinnyTheme ? 11 : 2,
                  color: Colors.white,
                  child: Container(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 12, horizontal: 9),
                    decoration: BoxDecoration(
                      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(20),
                      border: themeProvider.theme == fiinnyTheme
                          ? Border.all(color: Colors.blueAccent, width: 3)
                          : null,
                    ),
                    child: Column(
                      mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
                      children: [
                        Row(
                          mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
                          children: themeSwatches[fiinnyTheme]!
                              .map((color) => Container(
                                    margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 3),
                                    width: 23,
                                    height: 23,
                                    decoration: BoxDecoration(
                                      color: color,
                                      shape: BoxShape.circle,
                                      border: Border.all(color: Colors.grey.shade200, width: 1),
                                    ),
                                  ))
                              .toList(),
                        ),
                        const SizedBox(height: 14),
                        Text(
                          themeNames[fiinnyTheme]!,
                          style: TextStyle(
                            fontWeight: FontWeight.w600,
                            fontSize: 15.5,
                            color: Colors.black87,
                          ),
                        ),
                        if (themeProvider.theme == fiinnyTheme)
                          const Padding(
                            padding: EdgeInsets.only(top: 10),
                            child: Icon(Icons.check_circle, color: Colors.blueAccent),
                          ),
                      ],
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
              );
            }).toList(),
          ),
          const SizedBox(height: 8),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
